properties.headline: Flood Watch issued January 16 at 9:46AM CST until January 21 at 3:00AM CST by NWS Tulsa OK
properties.description:
...The National Weather Service in Tulsa has issued a Flood Watch for
the following rivers in Oklahoma...

Neosho River near Commerce affecting Ottawa County

The National Weather Service in Tulsa has issued a
* Flood Watch for
The Neosho River near Commerce
* until late Monday night.
* At  9:30 AM Thursday, the stage was 6.6 feet.
* Flood stage is 15.0 feet.
* Forecast...Flood stage may be exceeded this weekend if the rainfall
expected tonight through Friday occurs. Minor to moderate flooding
is possible. Continue to monitor later forecasts and remain alert for
possible warnings.
